Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.32,0:21:18.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙耶香
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.87,0:21:31.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  看不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.90,0:21:33.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了你还是缩着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.00,0:21:35.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来给你示范一下
