Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.15,0:21:40.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要妨碍我  我一个人能解决
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.42,0:21:45.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙耶香！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.94,0:21:53.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…  难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.85,0:22:10.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.82,0:22:13.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我有此意  痛觉什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.85,0:22:17.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是能够完全消除的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.56,0:22:25.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手  快住手
